Our Commitment to Fair Credit Practices
 LCV Steel Service Centre is dedicated to maintaining transparency and fairness in all our financial dealings. Our AI credit check system ensures that all assessments are conducted impartially and with respect to our clients' financial history while strictly adhering to data protection laws and safeguarding financial information.


Experian: Our Trusted Credit Information Partner
We partner with Experian, a global leader in credit reporting, to provide reliable and up-to-date credit information. With Experian's trusted data, we ensure that our financial assessments are both accurate and fair, helping us maintain strong relationships with our clients.

label: BREP HTML
name: Item-custom_brep_html
options:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/@google/model-viewer/dist/model-viewer.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        model-viewer {
            width: 100%;
            height: 600px;
            background-color: transparent; /* Fully transparent background */
        }

        /* ERPNext-like button styling */
        .erpnext-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            height: 30px; /* Ensure the button height matches the color picker */
            line-height: 14px; /* Vertical alignment of text */
        }

        .erpnext-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        input[type="color"] {
            height: 30px; /* Match the button height */
            padding: 0; /* Remove default padding */
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            vertical-align: middle; /* Align with the button */
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .controls {
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <model-viewer src="your-model.glb" alt="A 3D model" auto-rotate camera-controls id="modelViewer" class="outlined"></model-viewer>

    <script>
        modelViewer.addEventListener('load', () => {
            changeColor('#0048A1'); // Set the default color to blue after the model loads
        });
        function changeColor(color) {
            // const color = document.getElementById('colorPicker').value;
            const modelViewer = document.getElementById('modelViewer');
            const model = modelViewer.model;

            if (model) {
                const material = model.materials[0]; // Assumes the first material is the one to change
                material.pbrMetallicRoughness.setBaseColorFactor(hexToRgb(color));
            }
        }

        function hexToRgb(hex) {
            const bigint = parseInt(hex.slice(1), 16);
            const r = (bigint >> 16) & 255;
            const g = (bigint >> 8) & 255;
            const b = bigint & 255;
            return [r / 255, g / 255, b / 255, 1];
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
